ActNational Defence Act
Queen's Regulations and Orders for the Canadian Forces
SubjectReinstatement of a former non-commissioned member
PrecisOrder cancelling the release of Master Corporal ORMAN BOYD SAVAGE, a former non-commissioned member who was released as a result of being found guilty by a court, but was later found not guilty by a competent authority.
